# =============================================================================
# CODEOWNERS — review routing
#
# Each line: file pattern → GitHub username(s) or team(s)
# Matched top-to-bottom, last match wins.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
# =============================================================================

# Default — all changes require review from the team
# * @your-org/your-team

# Infrastructure modules — platform team owns these
# src/app/config/     @your-org/platform
# src/app/database/   @your-org/platform
# src/app/logging/    @your-org/platform
# src/app/errors/     @your-org/platform
# src/app/health/     @your-org/platform
# src/app/security/   @your-org/platform
# src/app/resilience/ @your-org/platform

# CI/CD
# .github/            @your-org/platform
# Dockerfile          @your-org/platform
# docker-compose.yml  @your-org/platform

# Migrations — require DBA or senior review
# migrations/         @your-org/dba
